OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FRemaining
OL,6,Fdry this evening with plenty of late
OL,7,Fevening sunshine. Overnight may see a
OL,8,Ffew mist patches reform but most
OL,9,Fremaining clear. Temperatures
OL,10,Fremaining high overnight and feeling
OL,11,Fvery warm.
OL,12,
OL,13,CSaturday:FThe heatwave continues on
OL,14,FSaturday with another dry and sunny
OL,15,Fday. Feeling hot with high UV but a
OL,16,Fmore notable breeze developing
OL,17,Fthroughout the day.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
