OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Sunday to Tuesday:
OL,6,FRemaining largely dry and sunny
OL,7,Fthroughout, although a small chance of
OL,8,Fthe odd thunderstorm developing from
OL,9,FMonday. Staying hot, although an
OL,10,Feasterly breeze will bring a little
OL,11,Frelief in places.
